<body>
    <h1>Assumptions</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1800" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"4=
449db81-00bc-407d-9f95-e58a05b9a8c2" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<colgroup>
<col style=3D"width: 119.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 1680.0px;">
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>S.no.</strong></p></td>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Assumption</strong></p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>1</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Oracle HCM Cloud is going to be an authoritative source application inte=
grated with the future state SailPoint IIQ platform.</p>
<p>All Associates, contingent workers and Non-Worker to be entered into Ora=
cle HCM prior to creating their SailPoint IIQ and AD accounts.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>2</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>The following are target systems that will be integrated with the SailPo=
int IAM platform as part of the Voyager scope:&nbsp;</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Oracle HCM Cloud</p></li>
<li>
<p>Active Directory(14)</p></li>
<li>
<p>ServiceNow</p></li>
<li>
<p>UKG</p></li>
<li>
<p>Oracle ERP Cloud</p></li>
<li>
<p>Oracle EPM Cloud</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Planning</p></li>
<li>
<p>Finance Consolidation and Close (FCCS)</p></li>
<li>
<p>Account Reconciliation (AR)</p></li>
<li>
<p>Oracle Enterprise Data Management Cloud Service (EDMCS)</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li>
<p>OCI</p></li>
<li>
<p>OIM</p></li>
<li>
<p>GSuite</p></li>
</ul></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>3</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Lower environments for Oracle HCM Cloud authoritative source and in-scop=
e target systems will be available for integration with non-prod IAM platfo=
rms for development, unit testing, SIT, UAT and additional testing purposes=
.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>4</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Effective change management processes will be in place to manage stakeho=
lder expectations, communicate project updates, and address resistance to c=
hange.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>5</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>PeopleSoft HR will be decommissioned as part of the Voyager program and =
will no longer exist in the system.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>6</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>The following applications, in addition to 270 disconnected applications=
, non-hr related quick links, Utility links, installed Plugins are carry fo=
rwarded as is and they are integrated with the existing Ascension Health Al=
liance=E2=80=99s SailPoint IdentityIQ platform and are working fine.</p>
<p><strong>Connected Application:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>AD-PRESENCEHEALTH (Active Directory - Direct)</p></li>
<li>
<p>AD-Archive (Active Directory - Direct)</p></li>
<li>
<p>AD-ACMHO (Active Directory - Direct)</p></li>
<li>
<p>AD-AHMFM (Active Directory - Direct)</p></li>
<li>
<p>AD-AHSCN (Active Directory - Direct)</p></li>
<li>
<p>AD-KSWIC (Active Directory - Direct)</p></li>
<li>
<p>AD-MIROC (Active Directory - Direct)</p></li>
<li>
<p>AD-OKTUL (Active Directory - Direct)</p></li>
<li>
<p>AD-WIAPP (Active Directory - Direct)</p></li>
<li>
<p>AD-WIGLE (Active Directory - Direct)</p></li>
<li>
<p>AD-AMITA (Active Directory - Direct)</p></li>
<li>
<p>AD-AID (Active Directory - Direct)</p></li>
<li>
<p>AD-ASC (Active Directory - Direct)</p></li>
<li>
<p>AD-DS (Active Directory - Direct)</p></li>
<li>
<p>Azure (Azure Active Directory)</p></li>
<li>
<p>Tableau - AscensionNational (Web Services)</p></li>
<li>
<p>Surgery Scheduling Manager (Web Services)</p></li>
<li>
<p>IN - Voalte (Web Services)</p></li>
<li>
<p>ININD - Sovera for HIM (JDBC)</p></li>
<li>
<p>SIEM Application (JDBC)</p></li>
<li>
<p>Doctor Master (JDBC)</p></li>
<li>
<p>Invision (JDBC)</p></li>
<li>
<p>Salesforce (Call Center) (Salesforce)</p></li>
<li>
<p>ServiceNow (ServiceNow)</p></li>
<li>
<p>TeamTSI (SQLLoader)</p></li>
<li>
<p>OneNurse (Logical)</p></li>
<li>
<p>GSuite (G Suite)</p></li>
<li>
<p>Duo (Duo)</p></li>
</ol>
<p><strong>Non-HR Quick Links:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"29">
<li>
<p>Manager Assignment</p></li>
<li>
<p>Manage Mailbox license</p></li>
<li>
<p>Enable Contractor</p></li>
<li>
<p>Extend Contractor Expiration Date</p></li>
<li>
<p>Create/Re-enable Non-HR Contractor</p></li>
<li>
<p>Update Workgroup</p></li>
<li>
<p>Manage Associate/Contractor</p></li>
<li>
<p>Modify Associate/Contractor</p></li>
<li>
<p>Immediate Disablement</p></li>
<li>
<p>View Identity (OOTB quick link)</p></li>
<li>
<p>Update Manual Term</p></li>
</ol>
<p><strong>Utility Links:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"40">
<li>
<p>AMITA Bulk Create</p></li>
<li>
<p>AMITA User Bulk Load Report</p></li>
</ol>
<p><strong>Installed Plugins:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"42">
<li>
<p>Hide Access Request Filters</p></li>
<li>
<p>SIEM Plugin</p></li>
<li>
<p>Support DataCollector Plugin</p></li>
<li>
<p>Message Of The Day</p></li>
<li>
<p>Object Exporter</p></li>
</ol></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>7</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Systems integrated with SailPoint IIQ are performing as expected without=
 issues.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>8</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>The existing Ascension Health Alliance SailPoint IIQ platform is functio=
ning as expected.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>9</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Duo access for MFA will be provisioned based on the AD group provisionin=
g through SailPoint.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>10</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>For error handling and request approval flows the existing process will =
be followed.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>11</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>PeopleSoft FSCM account provisioning will be handled through OIM and Sai=
lPoint provides a feed file to OIM. Person IDs will be synced to FSCM via a=
nother mechanism.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>12</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Person IDs in Oracle HCM Cloud will be the same as emplids in Peoplesoft=
 HCM.</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
    </div>
